## Secrets — never commit files with real keys/passwords
.env.production          # real runtime secrets (Jwt__Key, DB password, etc.)
.env.*.local
appsettings.*.local.json # local overrides with real credentials
# appsettings.Production.json is safe to commit — secrets injected via env vars

